Package: com.mikey820.tweetdownloader
Name: TweetDownloader
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Always-on, one-tap, best-quality media downloader for Twitter/X. Adds a download button at the top-right of every tweet with media; saves photos at :orig quality and videos at the highest-bitrate mp4 straight to the camera roll, no confirmation, with a download percentage at the top-left.
Maintainer: mikey820
Author: mikey820
Section: Tweaks
